# Client-side Vite env vars (baked into the browser bundle at build time).
# NEVER put real secrets here — everything here is shipped to end users.
# Copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill in the values.

# ─── Cloudflare Turnstile ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Site key for the CAPTCHA widget on /auth/sign-up. The widget reads this via
# `import.meta.env.VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY` and refuses to render if missing,
# which leaves the "Create account" button permanently disabled.
#
# For LOCAL DEV: use Cloudflare's documented test key below — it auto-passes
# without showing a challenge. Pair it with the matching test SECRET key in
# `apps/web/.dev.vars` (see `.dev.vars.example`).
#
# For PRODUCTION: register a real site at
# https://dash.cloudflare.com/?to=/:account/turnstile and replace both keys.
#
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/turnstile/troubleshooting/testing/
VITE_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=1x00000000000000000000AA
